# Paste relevant sections into ~/.mbsyncrc
# The proxy handles OAuth2; mbsync only needs basic IMAP AUTH on localhost.

IMAPAccount outlook-proxy
  Host 127.0.0.1
  Port 1143
  User youremail@outlook.com
  Pass anything_proxy_ignores_this
  TLSType None
  AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore outlook-remote
  Account outlook-proxy

MaildirStore outlook-local
  SubFolders Verbatim
  Path ~/Mail/Outlook/
  Inbox ~/Mail/Outlook/Inbox

Channel outlook
  Far :outlook-remote:
  Near :outlook-local:
  Patterns *
  Create Both
  Expunge None
  SyncState *
